reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars New Favorite Charging Cords
reviews.reviewText: I bought these after the usual charging cords I typically used died again, and I noticed that the lifespan of those weren’t as good as it used to be so I decided to shop around. I came across these and as long as the performance doesn’t change, I will continue to buy them. I love the different lengths, the price and the colors are a nice bonus. They’re great, charge our devices rather quickly, too. Definitely will be buying more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Burst of Color and Quality - 5 Stars!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the 6-pack of colorful cables, and I couldn't be happier with my purchase! Here's why I gave it a well-deserved 5-star rating:1. Vibrant Pastel Colors:The pastel colors of these cables are simply stunning! They add a pop of brightness to my space and make it easy to identify each cable at a glance. It's a small detail, but it makes a big difference, especially if you're like me and have multiple devices plugged in. Also prevents your aunt from walking away with your cable LOL!2. Great Quality:I was pleasantly surprised by the quality of these cables. The connectors are sturdy, and the cables themselves feel durable. I've had issues with flimsy cables in the past, but these seem like they'll withstand the test of time. No more dealing with frayed or unreliable charging cables! I like that they are thicker then the original apple ones as well!3. Excellent Price:Considering the quality and the fact that it's a 6-pack, the price is unbeatable. I've seen similar cables sold individually for the same price as this entire pack! It's a fantastic deal that doesn't compromise on quality. I feel like I got more than my money's worth with this purchase.4. Variety of Sizes:The variety of sizes in this pack is a game-changer. From short cables for when I'm sitting right next to an outlet, to longer ones for when I need a little more flexibility, this pack has it all. It's convenient and ensures that I always have the right cable for the job.In conclusion, I highly recommend this 6-pack of colorful cables. The pastel colors are delightful, the quality is top-notch, the price is unbeatable, and the variety of sizes is incredibly convenient. It's a win-win-win-win situation! If you're in need of reliable and visually appealing cables, look no further. This purchase exceeded my expectations, and I'm one happy customer!

reviews.reviewText: I bought these chargers because all of my other ones stopped working at the same time.
